於\r\n判決送達後20日內補提上訴理由書（須附繕本）。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　1 　　月　　19　　日\r\n\r\n                                  書記官　黃舜民","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCEV/110%2c%e4%b8%ad%e5%b0%8f%2c4535%2c20220119%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCEV,110,中小,4535,20220119,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"中小","JNO":"4535","JDATE":"20220119","JTITLE":"返還借款"}